  "detailed_description": "Immerse yourself in the future battlegrounds of \"Silicon War:Blitz\"，fighting shoulder to shoulder with your mech！<br>Feel the rush of speed and evasion, navigate through relentless bullet barrages, and make precise shots in fierce combat to carve out a chance for survival.<br>Embrace strategy and choice, along with growth and upgrades. Every decision you make is a step toward your own legend.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Shoot 'em up</h2>Brush past a relentless deluge of bullets, seeking ways to survive and strike back. Steadfastly hold the line  against the mightiest of foes!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780310/extras/2679eefd332b42957f58ba9afa81889f.poster.avif?t=1724897992\" width=408 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780310/extras/2679eefd332b42957f58ba9afa81889f.webm?t=1724897992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780310/extras/2679eefd332b42957f58ba9afa81889f.mp4?t=1724897992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pilot a mech</h2>Pilot your mech and dive into the frontline , adeptly maneuvering through the chaotic, ever-changing battlefield while dodging hazards at breakneck speeds!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780310/extras/c829370cabd96bc2300aabdde354f6e2.poster.avif?t=1724897992\" width=408 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780310/extras/c829370cabd96bc2300aabdde354f6e2.webm?t=1724897992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780310/extras/c829370cabd96bc2300aabdde354f6e2.mp4?t=1724897992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roguelite</h2>Each game is a new challenge.  Delve into a world of endless possibilities with diverse buff combinations，crafting new and dynamic experiences every time！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780310/extras/c32c42e5af4d55e497acb96c04ab3560.poster.avif?t=1724897992\" width=408 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780310/extras/c32c42e5af4d55e497acb96c04ab3560.webm?t=1724897992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780310/extras/c32c42e5af4d55e497acb96c04ab3560.mp4?t=1724897992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build-up</h2>Accumulate resources in battle, unleash powerful upgrades and equip weapon slots in your hangar，making your mech more formidable than ever！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780310/extras/fdf90b94721e1e0783e725dab7e357fb.poster.avif?t=1724897992\" width=408 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780310/extras/fdf90b94721e1e0783e725dab7e357fb.webm?t=1724897992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780310/extras/fdf90b94721e1e0783e725dab7e357fb.mp4?t=1724897992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
